    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved; the upholstery is free of tears, and all electronic features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully functional. Mechanically, it has been regularly serviced and drives smoothly, though the tires will likely need replacing within the next year. Overall, it's a dependable and attractive car that offers great value for its next owner.",
