    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to the highest standards, manifesting in a condition that is indistinguishable from its original production state. Every detail, from the pristine interior finishes to the flawless exterior luster, confirms a history of meticulous stewardship. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the individual who demands excellence without compromise. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
