    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. The interior is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather remains supple and matte, the high-gloss trim is free of micro-scratches, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions with precision, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule example for the buyer who demands perfection and refuses to compromise on quality. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its model line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
