      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
